{"tid":1043173,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日終於要離開中學了","createTime":"2019-03-02T05:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T06:16:48.000Z","uid":165988,"like":5,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e414d469cc9a5f1ed4985eb05cde537d29a3602c","tid":1043173,"uid":165988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:25:27.000Z","msg":"琴日學校last day,正式離開校門嗰下其實都冇咩特別大感覺，直到食完班飯番到屋企之後，睇番同班fd嘅合照，真係好撚想喊，諗到以後都冇得日日見面，由上堂傾偈傾到落堂，真係愈諗愈傷心，畢業之後仲keep唔keep到關係都係未知之數，本身我係出面就冇朋友，唯一嘅朋友都喺哂學校，畢業，即係代表連依班fd都可能會冇埋，番工嘅番工，讀書嘅讀書，見面時間一定會變到好少好少，以後就得番自己一個生活，諗到都覺得一定係會好枯燥乏味<br />\n   琴晚真係連瞓都瞓唔著，今日啲時間又好似停頓咗咁，仿佛生存都好似冇咩意義真係好想番去三年前啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲讀緊中學嘅巴打們，真係要珍惜眼前人啊"},{"pid":"6a106de4b0d2ff371ce4fc2842b4f8d340cb09fe","tid":1043173,"uid":165988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204ed62a84bf002afffede6bebb24428971abe45","tid":1043173,"uid":121431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:41:28.000Z","msg":"上到大學你先講啦"},{"pid":"f31121b7e5b36d1069483a40dcb779d8b41166f1","tid":1043173,"uid":165988,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"204ed62a84bf002afffede6bebb24428971abe45","tid":1043173,"uid":121431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:41:28.000Z","msg":"上到大學你先講啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:49:45.000Z","msg":"大學fd有可能可以好似中學fd咁close咩，同埋我決定咗唔讀大學"},{"pid":"3293a66de169995b5e90cdd472d92582e9f64ba6","tid":1043173,"uid":195975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T05:53:09.000Z","msg":"2年lu 中學同學都好耐冇見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a80c3096f242f0a878a53c60a67d22374f2c2a8","tid":1043173,"uid":165988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3293a66de169995b5e90cdd472d92582e9f64ba6","tid":1043173,"uid":195975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor